data.description: Looking for comfy bedrooms, lots of closet space with just enough of the hard work done leaving you to just the details you want? Conveniently on the outskirts of Tyler, in New Chapel Hill ISD, this home is country living with city convenience. This 3/2 sits on 1/2 acre overlooking the gorgeous surroundings of a hay meadow and trees. The all electric ranch style has a 2 car garage, interior laundry, a 20x20 carport, 16x14 wood shed, and a 24x12 older metal shed.
